    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use Twisted Chakra to generate a large barrier. All creatures of your choice in range other than you are treated as if they are sharing in all Twisted Hit Points you currently have left and become immune to the damage and all associated effects while you still have Twisted Hit Points.</p><p>If multiple creatures would take damage from a single casting of a jutsu or effect, you instead take the highest instance of damage, reducing your Twisted Hit Points by the result.</p>",
